params.name: callback
params.description: Function to call for each item. Arguments passed: current key, current item, dictionary.

core.each.shortDescription: Iterate over each key in a dictionary, where each key is a propery of the dictionary.

params.name: target
params.description: Target to unpack to. Default is `window`.

core.unpack.longDescription: The target will have the key-value pairs appended, or overwritten if the key-value pair already exists.
core.unpack.shortDescription: Unpack a dictionary to a target.
